name: Parking Jam (itch) (m2loveq1)
description: Parking Jam is a fast-paced and challenging puzzle game. The goal is to maneuver a series of vehicles in a crowded parking lot and free the trapped car by moving other vehicles out of the way. Players must think strategically and plan their moves in advance to successfully solve each level. With increasing levels of difficulty, players will need to use quick thinking and precise movements to progress through the game. With its intuitive controls and addictive gameplay, Parking Jam is a fun and engaging game for players of all ages.
